# в”Җв”Җв”Җ Show current status в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
show_status() {
  print_header "Current Status"

  if agent_loaded; then
    local sched
    sched=$(get_schedule_description)
    print_success "LaunchAgent is loaded"
    echo -e "  Schedule : ${BOLD}${sched}${NC}"
  else
    print_warning "LaunchAgent is not loaded"
  fi

  echo -e "  Path     : ${BOLD}${REPO_DIR}${NC}"
  echo -e "  Repo     : ${BOLD}$(short_repo)${NC}"

  # Show file counts
  if [ -d "$REPO_DIR" ]; then
    local formula_count=0 cask_count=0 mas_count=0
    [ -f "$REPO_DIR/brewlist-formula.txt" ] && formula_count=$(wc -l < "$REPO_DIR/brewlist-formula.txt" | tr -d ' ')
    [ -f "$REPO_DIR/brewlist-cask.txt" ] && cask_count=$(wc -l < "$REPO_DIR/brewlist-cask.txt" | tr -d ' ')
    [ -f "$REPO_DIR/maslist.txt" ] && mas_count=$(wc -l < "$REPO_DIR/maslist.txt" | tr -d ' ')
    echo -e "  Formulae : ${BOLD}${formula_count}${NC}"
    echo -e "  Casks    : ${BOLD}${cask_count}${NC}"
    echo -e "  MAS apps : ${BOLD}${mas_count}${NC}"
  fi

  echo ""
  read -r -p "Press Enter to continue..." && clear_up 1
}

# в”Җв”Җв”Җ Disable в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
do_disable() {
  # Unload LaunchAgent if active
  if agent_loaded || [ -f "$PLIST_FILE" ]; then
    unload_agent
  else
    print_warning "LaunchAgent is not active"
  fi

  # Handle the package list directory
  if [ -d "$REPO_DIR" ]; then
    echo ""
    echo -e "  ${PINK}>${NC} ${GREEN}1)${NC} Delete directory and files (${REPO_DIR})"
    echo -e "  ${PINK}>${NC} ${GREEN}2)${NC} Keep directory"
    echo -e "  ${PINK}>${NC} ${GREEN}3)${NC} Cancel"
    echo ""
    read -r -p "$(echo -e "${BRIGHT_PINK}Choose [1-3]:${NC} ")" dir_choice
    clear_up 6

    case "$dir_choice" in
      1)
        rm -rf "$REPO_DIR"
        print_success "Deleted ${REPO_DIR}"
        REPO_DIR=""
        REMOTE_URL=""
        save_config
        ;;
      2)
        print_warning "Directory kept at ${REPO_DIR}"
        ;;
      *)
        print_warning "Cancelled"
        ;;
    esac
  else
    echo ""
    echo -e "  ${YELLOW}Directory ${REPO_DIR} does not exist.${NC}"
    echo ""
    echo -e "  ${PINK}>${NC} ${GREEN}1)${NC} Update config (directory was moved/removed)"
    echo -e "  ${PINK}>${NC} ${GREEN}2)${NC} Cancel"
    echo ""
    read -r -p "$(echo -e "${BRIGHT_PINK}Choose [1-2]:${NC} ")" dir_choice
    clear_up 6

    case "$dir_choice" in
      1)
        REPO_DIR=""
        REMOTE_URL=""
        save_config
        print_success "Config cleared вҖ” re-run brewsync to set up again"
        ;;
      *)
        print_warning "Cancelled"
        ;;
    esac
  fi

  echo ""
  read -r -p "Press Enter to continue..." && clear_up 1
}

